scope_1_comments: Quote from CDP response 'Yara Business Unit Carbon Dioxide ( BUCO2). Yara Industrialis one of four divisions of Yara International. Yara Industrial market nitrogen based chemicals, sourced primarily from Yara's fertiliser production plants, to non agricultural customers. Within the Industrial Division, Business Unit CO2 markets liquid carbon dioxide and dry-ice in Western Europe and Scandinavia. The production assets are located in a number of countries and liquid carbon dioxide is supplied across borders by road tanker and ship. The emissions data is relevant for the Business Unit Operation as an entity, not for individual countries. This response is only relevant for Business Unit CO2, not Yara Industrial or Yara International.'
